hopobject.body: I'm a housewife koshland pharmacy jobs “The government here is young, smart and has a clear strategy,” says Kieran Kelleher of Savills Montenegro. “Wherever five-star hotels go, property prices follow, and at last hotels are coming. There is 2bn Euros of high-quality investment planned over the next few years. I don’t know anywhere else in Europe with these kinds of numbers. It is going to transform the area. Buyers are taking a punt on what Kotor will be like in five years time, and I think it could be quite incredible.”
